org.spongepowered.api.event.cause.entity.health.source

Interface EntityHealingSource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HealingSource
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IndirectEntityHealingSource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractEntityHealingSource

    public interface EntityHealingSource
extends HealingSource
    Signifies that the healing source is another entity, can usually mean that the healing source is the same entity being healed. Examples may include self healing from Boss entities, Witches, etc.
